{"word":"συμπνίγω","slug":"συμπνίγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συμπνίγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πνίγω\">πνίγω</a></el>] ‘obstruct or constrict by pressure’, <b>choke<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> seed that is germinating <b><a href='B:480 4:7'>Mk 4:7</a>;</b> seed personified <b><a href='B:490 8:14'>Lk 8:14</a>;</b> the divine message <b><a href='B:470 13:22'>Mt 13:22</a>; <a href='B:480 4:19'>Mk 4:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in dramatic hyperbole, of hemming in a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> by crowd pressure <b><a href='B:490 8:42'>Lk 8:42</a>; <a href='B:490 12:1'>12:1</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συμπληρόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συμπολίτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}